{"tid":1936714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【引退一年】吉澤明步出自傳公開16年AV史","createTime":"2020-03-21T11:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T02:59:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf8e319c738076c4078b801025218981b2b0e74","tid":1936714,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"有「暗黑Stephy」之稱的36歲前日本AV天后吉澤明步，去年3月宣布從良引退，令不少男粉絲大感可惜。離開AV界一年的她，宣布將於本月31日推出自傳《單體女優》，剖白過去16年的AV女優生涯。<br />\n<br />\n吉澤明步於18歲入行，演出的AV作品超過500部，人氣遍及中、港、台。她在自傳中透露當年瞞住父母演出AV，曝光後曾遭到雙親激烈反對，入行以來她又曾有過四名男友。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200321/bkn-20200321075709768-0321_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200321%2Fbkn-20200321075709768-0321_00862_001.html&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92Fze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=099deaf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200321/bkn-20200321075709768-0321_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e32f058c1c9ee942b1b47ae99515a2c39250724a","tid":1936714,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"有冇講屎塔肥同万刀甲？"},{"pid":"9ff55f1ff760726b9cf228af32fff1bdc187333a","tid":1936714,"uid":96512,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fI9Pvwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfI9Pvwu.jpg&h=ae1ba5d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aaf2c95235e2ac4397e8fae8cf089d0181d99cf","tid":1936714,"uid":73467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ff55f1ff760726b9cf228af32fff1bdc187333a","tid":1936714,"uid":96512,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fI9Pvwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfI9Pvwu.jpg&h=ae1ba5d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re